@proto = http
@host = localhost
@port = 3000
@api_prefix = /api
@docs_prefix = /api/docs

### 1. 列表查询 - 全部文档 (默认)
GET {{proto}}://{{host}}:{{port}}{{docs_prefix}}

### 1.1 列表查询 - 按名称搜索
GET {{proto}}://{{host}}:{{port}}{{docs_prefix}}?name=drizzle

### 1.2 列表查询 - 热门文档 (Trending)
GET {{proto}}://{{host}}:{{port}}{{docs_prefix}}?type=trending

### 1.3 列表查询 - 我的收藏 (Favorites)
# 需要 x-role: user 并且系统能获取到 userId，这里模拟 header，实际可能需要 jwt
GET {{proto}}://{{host}}:{{port}}{{docs_prefix}}?type=favorites
x-role: user

### 2. 添加文档索引
POST {{proto}}://{{host}}:{{port}}{{docs_prefix}}/add
Content-Type: application/json
x-role: user

{
  "url": "https://github.com/fkcaikengren/uni-hooks",
  "docName": "uni-hooks"
}

### 3. 收藏/取消收藏文档
# 假设 slug 为 github_fkcaikengren_create-mcp
POST {{proto}}://{{host}}:{{port}}{{docs_prefix}}/github_fkcaikengren_create-mcp/favorite
Content-Type: application/json
x-role: user

{
  "like": true
}

### 3.1 取消收藏
POST {{proto}}://{{host}}:{{port}}{{docs_prefix}}/github_drizzle_team_drizzle-orm/favorite
Content-Type: application/json
x-role: user

{
  "like": false
}

### 4. 增加访问计数 (Check)
POST {{proto}}://{{host}}:{{port}}{{docs_prefix}}/github_fkcaikengren_uni-hooks/check
x-role: guest

### 5. 获取 LLM 上下文文本 (llm.txt)
GET {{proto}}://{{host}}:{{port}}{{docs_prefix}}/github_fkcaikengren_uni-hooks/llm.txt?topic=uni-hooks&tokens=1000

### 6. 查询文档片段 (Query)
GET {{proto}}://{{host}}:{{port}}{{docs_prefix}}/github_fkcaikengren_uni-hooks/query?topic=uni-hooks&tokens=1000
